body:
I'm attempting to use a Dataset as you recommended, but now I am getting a
new error that says " ValueError: Duplicate node name in graph: 'packed'".

I am trying to convert the MNIST data to a tensor, select subsets of the
training data into lists, convert the lists into tensors, and then convert
the "list" tensors into datasets.

However, the classifier.train command is still not working.

Do you have any suggestions on how to fix this or would you recommend I try
a different strategy?

Thank you.
